docs.text:
Field Value Purpose <code>address</code> <code>whitelisted-cdn-domain.com</code> DNS resolution target (fronted domain) <code>port</code> <code>80</code> Must be HTTP to bypass SNI check <code>Host</code> header <code>proxy.yourdomain.com</code> Your CloudFront CNAME (actual routing) <code>path</code> <code>/ws-path</code> WebSocket endpoint on Xray server <pre><code>{
  "outbounds": [
    {
      "protocol": "vmess",
      "settings": {
        "vnext": [
          {
            "address": "whitelisted-cdn-domain.com",
            "port": 80,
            "users": [
              {
                "id": "your-uuid-here",
                "alterId": 0,
                "security": "none"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "streamSettings": {
        "network": "ws",
        "wsSettings": {
          "path": "/ws-path",
          "headers": {
            "Host": "proxy.yourdomain.com"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
</code></pre>
